5000|$|Aeronautical mobile (OR) service (short: AMS; &#124; also: {{aeronautical}} {{mobile radiocommunication}} service) is - according to Article 1.34 of the International Telecommunication Union´s (ITU) Radio Regulations (RR) - defined as «An <b>aeronautical</b> <b>mobile</b> <b>service</b> intended for communications, including those relating to flight coordination, primarily outside national or international civil air routes.» ...|$|E
