50|$|The AN/ARC-164 is a {{military}} airborne UHF radio station that operates in the <b>aeronautical</b> <b>mobile</b> (OR) <b>service.</b> It might be found on B-52G/H, B-1B, C/EC/RC-26D, KC-135, C-23, C-130, C-141, F-15, A-10, F-16, UH-1D, CH-47, H-53, H-60 and S-3B aircraft.|$|R
